{"type": "article", "id": 58595, "title": "一套六角形桌面收纳产品，材料和结构比例都很讲究｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-22T23:12:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54484, "name": "CEDIT – ceramiche d’italia"}, {"id": 54485, "name": "Studio Formafantasma"}, {"id": 15888, "name": "本土创造"}, {"id": 54486, "name": "Coalesse"}, {"id": 54487, "name": "Lievore Altherr Molina"}, {"id": 54488, "name": "Viccarbe"}, {"id": 809, "name": "Vitra"}, {"id": 21209, "name": "Max Voytenko"}, {"id": 939, "name": "Jasper Morrison"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 87, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181122200317Bi1HedOzXJ2PvQIq.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s4 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #141414} span.s9 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s10 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s11 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s12 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hexagonal Containers by Jasper Morrison + Vitra</h3><p>英国极简主义设计大师 Jasper Morrison 与瑞士家具大厂合作频繁，已推出数十件产品。最近，双方又合力推出办公桌面收纳产品，目的是为凌乱的办公桌面提供解决方案。</p><p>Jasper Morrison 着力于材料和比例的组合，设计了六角形容器，用于存放钢笔、铅笔、尺子、橡皮、回形针以及其他微小杂物，使其条理化地存放于用户的桌面上。</p><p>这一系列外形紧凑的陶瓷容器有三个高度，每个都有六个侧面，可以在办公室或家庭办公桌上以任意数量配置，整齐地排列在一起。六角形容器有三件套，有三种颜色可供选择，包括深绿色、橙色或浅灰色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200348QUNliIuqSkvdwRTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200349me7rWsXjdwk8I56J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.586000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200350wzWvxa5FRilHgkMD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.615000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200350L6e8CMd0jmUz9P4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200350loMGAnEwezxybgCF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621094\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.vitra.com/en-us/living/product/details/hexagonal-containers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vitra</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sistema Lounge System by Viccarbe &amp; Lievore Altherr Molina for Coalesse</h3><p>设计品牌 Coalesse 在北美市场推出了一套可定制的休息室系统 Sistema，设计制造方是西班牙公司 Viccarbe 和西班牙设计工作室 Lievore Altherr Molina。</p><p>这一系列模块化座椅系列可以通过多种方式进行定制，从靠背高度到底座选项，甚至是颜色、面料、木材和其他细节，希望能够帮助用户实现更多自我表达的可能性。</p><p>Sistema 系统基于软垫方形座椅模块设计，它提供了各种颜色的金属圆筒和剪刀式支腿，以及比以前更多的纺织面料选项。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200433tGsQd90cqLFfJlE1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200434D5n6btPVOszmqfw9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200435Zpk2dV8q3jnvUGmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.699239\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200436z8gJimThYdRXWrGy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.344484\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811222004374ZCsnkpErNw5dObY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.coalesse.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coalesse</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>水磨石系列吊灯“金” by 本土创造</h3><p>原创设计品牌本土创造推出水磨石系列新品吊灯——“金”，白中缀黑，清新别致；黑中点白，神秘巧妙。</p><p>细腻斑驳的水磨石肌理跃然于上，为沉稳内敛的经典外型注入灵动气息。亮灯时，简洁的线条愈加分明利落，非黑即白的刻板与清冷此时被灯光调适得柔和而温润。黑白基调化繁为简，满足照明功能的同时，令装饰重点和视觉聚焦回归空间本身，与日常同化，融入各类空间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200515MO3askG6YzJrWKgI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200516lTKvHNJ0zYWDtO3C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200516ojULTmQsHNtgacwF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200517s49fd85vjnIBNEUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200518rGdEVxNX1yjw9Kbz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200518WgJu5wz6KStrRUvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.402778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200519Ww1SvnjALbDfI9UJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.bentudesign.com/CN/product.asp?b_classid=127\" rel=\"nofollow\">本土创造</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cromatica by Studio Formafantasma for CEDIT – ceramiche d’italia</h3><p>studio formafantasma 近日为 CEDIT 品牌设计了 Cromatica 瓷砖系列，将明快的色彩与独具魅力的深度展现给大家。这一系列不仅参考了制造的传统，使用的独特手法还在创造出完美工艺的基础上提供了多种个性化组合方式。</p><p>CEDIT 此次推出的 Cromatica 系列也标志着瓷砖在建筑行业中的应用趋势的变化，即需要的瓷砖尺寸越来越大，瓷砖色彩越来越鲜艳。这种现代的生产流程消除了出现不必要瑕疵的可能性，同时也赋予每块瓷砖独有的个性。利用 Cromatica 系列，Studio Formafantasma 也深入探索了现代陶瓷制造中色彩变化的潜能。</p><p>“这次我们使用了 Ettore sottsass 在 1980 年代为 CEDIT 专门创造的色板，并将这个色板视作设计开发的起点，” Studio Formafantasma 设计师 Andrea Trimarchi 与 Simone Farresin 表示。设计者将 Sottsass 当年推出的 41 色亮面瓷砖精简至 Cromatica 系列的六款配色，同时有自然和光滑两种表面可供选择。通过提升一系列全新技术，这些独特的色彩让每块瓷砖都拥有了全新的色调与变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200619XY4RjlcZ87upVvPx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200622qX2nFksytadT4NDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200623lA2ng8WUB5VFy3YD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200623ysgw5bPoc4jSWdhN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018112220062485c0rkOZVYIvPRUw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200624btNKc4hQZpl3S8eH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200625BFGAUdZWxLy8K2gR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200625H4IuDUylAT7f9a0Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.709046\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fold Tables by Max Voytenko </h3><p>Fold 桌子系列是对 1970 年代设计风格的致敬，最大限度地增强了极简主义的美学外观，出自乌克兰设计师 Max Voytenko 之手。</p><p>他的灵感来自于一张纸的弯曲形式，期待为桌子和周边空间带来意想不到的轻盈感，当然也简洁实现了其多功能的元素。</p><p>两款咖啡桌可用于两个不同的位置，用于起居室的多种家具解决方案。另有一款桌子可以用作茶几。它们可以组合使用，也可以单独陈列，样式简单，却足够引人注目。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200651yg8OXVvWc56f4sa9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200652snaXxMKe6Gl0gJyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811222006525QxM94LF3OWqUeE7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181122200653fjLnF8DMi1NvlOct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.maxvoytenko.com/fold-tables/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Max Voytenko</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}